original: You were reading a book near Ruby Street in Middle Park yesterday.  Long dark hair, jeans, Bull Emic top.  All I did was sit next to you and smell your hair.  Why so jumpy?    Let's work through your issues together.  Maybe I was taking things too fast.  Give me a second chance????
translated: 你昨天在中心公园的Ruby街附近看书。黑色的长发，穿着牛仔裤和Bull Emic的上衣。不就是坐到你旁边闻了下头发吗，反应那么大干嘛？让我帮你解决这个问题吧。也许是我操之过急了。再给我一个机会吧？？？？
